Inserted: Data = 20, Priority = 1
Inserted: Data = 30, Priority = 2
Inserted: Data = 40, Priority = 5
Data    Priority
20      1
30      2
10      3
40      5
Deleted highest priority: 20
Data    Priority
30      2
10      3
40      5
```

