**(b)** Write a C program to implement a circular queue of integers using an array of size 6. Include `enqueue`, `dequeue`, and `display` operations. Show the output for the sequence: `enqueue(5), enqueue(10), enqueue(15), enqueue(20), dequeue(), enqueue(25), enqueue(30)`. *(7 marks)*

