#### ✦ Question B (14 Marks) `[KTU University Exam – Dec 2023]`

**a)** Explain the **structure of a doubly linked list**. Write C functions to perform **insertion at the beginning** and **deletion from the end** of a doubly linked list. **(7 marks)**

**b)** Write a C function to **reverse a singly linked list** by changing the link directions. Trace the algorithm with an example list `10 → 20 → 30 → 40`. **(7 marks)**

