| **Empty List** | `NULL` | Insert 5 | `5 → 5` (self-loop) | `head = newNode` |
| **Single Node** | `5 → 5` | Insert 10 at end | `5 → 10 → 5` | Last traversal stops at `head` |
| **Multi Node — Front** | `10 → 20 → 30 → 10` | Insert 5 at front | `5 → 10 → 20 → 30 → 5` | Head changes |
| **Multi Node — End** | `10 → 20 → 30 → 10` | Insert 40 at end | `10 → 20 → 30 → 40 → 10` | Head unchanged |
| **Multi Node — Position 2** | `10 → 20 → 30 → 10` | Insert 15 at pos 2 | `10 → 15 → 20 → 30 → 10` | Re-link in middle |

