### **Question 2: [KTU University Exam – Dec 2022, May 2023]**
**Differentiate between BFS and DFS in terms of data structure used and order of traversal.**

**Model Answer (3 marks):**

| Aspect | BFS | DFS |
|---|---|---|
| **Data Structure** | Queue (FIFO) — First In, First Out | Stack (LIFO) — Last In, First Out (or recursion) |
| **Order of Traversal** | Level-by-level (breadth-wise expansion) | Branch-by-branch (deepest path first, then backtrack) |
| **Backtracking** | Does not backtrack — explores all neighbors first | Backtracks upon reaching a dead-end |

